Although your hands are deft and five yrs of Catholic school taught nothing if not how to be discreet; Ms Greene has a keen eye and catches your pilfering with a disapproving look. She pardons herself from the mystery guest and much to your dismay walks your way. “I couldn’t help noticing how much you enjoy my scones. Perhaps next time you’d consider that there are other guests here as well?”

What do you want to do?
